com/s?q=%E9%85%B5%E7%B4%A0&amp;src=newstranscode" class="qkw">酵素</a>及植物提取物为肌肤提供能量，有效改善肌肤状态，长期熬夜的妹纸不妨用起来。</p><p>完美底妆篇:化妆最担心的是什么，起皮、油光、脱妆!所以在粉底液的选择上，要尽量水漾质地，避免出油爆皮。【SULWHASOO】采淡致美气垫粉底液亮白系列，是一款透气、轻薄型气垫粉底液，拥有持久遮瑕力，可打造自然无暇底妆。【HERA】UV保湿气垫粉饼，兼具持久力与高遮瑕力的保湿气垫粉饼，水水的，使用之后没有上妆的感觉，即使在潮湿的环境中也能保持12小时不脱妆。</p><p><img src="http://p31.qhimg.com/t01fa23545ef6e59e89.jpg?size=1383x497"></p></div>  <footer>  <p class=tip_quick>文章内容由搜索引擎自动发现并显示为快照，不代表360新闻的立场和观点，<a target=_blank class=viewsource href="http://www.heb.chinanews.com/65/2015-06-16/2612.html">查看原文</a></p>      </footer> </article> <section class=sohu_cy> <div id=SOHUCS sid='99966023b19464af75ce278bfb5a5fe8'></div><script id=changyan_mobile_js charset="utf-8" src="http://changyan.sohu.com/upload/mobile/wap-js/changyan_mobile.js?client_id=cyrTywwWs&conf=prod_c56aa5a54e89138d855c5ca9b31470a0" ></script> </section>  <aside id="next-news"> <h3><em>pony</em>的其它新闻:</h3> <ul>    <li> <a href="/transcode?q=pony&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=9&amp;m=ba7bcd3b1d1f486ed626610474d16628c86231dc&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.zol.com.cn%2F512%2F5128703.html" data-pos="1"> 谷歌将推出Gmail支付服务<b>Pony</b> Express </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=pony&amp;pn=1&amp;pos=10&amp;m=0e247a7024e771dffee3f67fce960f2ddaad2f2a&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Ffashion.sohu.com%2F20150208%2Fn408846152.shtml" data-pos="2"> 【美丽姐】<b>pony</b>天气图案完美仿妆 </a>   <li> <a href="/transcode?q=pony&amp;pn=2&amp;pos=1&amp;m=03eb64f51494a1cd4ec4f4883a12c2ba471ed7bc&amp;u=http%3A%2F%2Ffashion.sohu.com%2F20141121%2Fn406251200.shtml" data-pos="3"> 【__邹邹__】<b>Pony</b> 俏皮仿妆 </a>  </ul> </aside>  <div class=mask style="display:none"></div> <div class="open-in-browser-tip" style="display:none"> <p>好无奈，微信君不让直接下载，别担心，点击<b>右上角</b>，选择“<b>在浏览器中打开</b>”就能下载啦~</p> <a class=close href="javascript:;"><img src="http://p3.qhimg.com/d/inn/a8960a66/close.png"></a> </div><script>(function(){var e=document.getElementById("news-body"),t=e.getElementsByTagName("img");for(var n=0;n<t.length;n++)t[n].parentNode.tagName.toUpperCase()==="P"